OL,3,C'He was a baby': Sister of US soldier,
OL,4,C20, killed in Kuwait pays tribute
OL,6,FThe sister of a 20-year-old US service
OL,7,Fmember killed within the opening hours
OL,8,Fof war with Iran has shared her
OL,9,Fdevastation at his death just two
OL,10,Fmonths before his 21st birthday.
OL,12,FSgt. Declan J. Coady was on his first
OL,13,Fdeployment in Kuwait when he was one
OL,14,Fof six Americans killed by a drone
OL,15,Fstrike on a civilian port on March 1.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
