OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772716281
OL,3,C'He was a baby': Sister of US soldier,
OL,4,C20, killed in Kuwait pays tribute
OL,6,F"He was really strong, he never let
OL,7,Fhis emotions really show. But I can't
OL,8,Fhelp that think because he was my
OL,9,Flittle brother he was probably really
OL,10,Fscared, even if he didn't want people
OL,11,Fto know," Keira Coady said tearfully
OL,12,Foutside the family's home in West Des
OL,13,FMoines, Iowa.
OL,15,F"I just wish he could have known one
OL,16,Fmore time that we all loved him.
OL,17,FBecause he was so amazing and kind."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
