OL,3,C'He was a baby': Sister of US soldier,
OL,4,C20, killed in Kuwait pays tribute
OL,6,FAll of the US service members killed
OL,7,Fwere part of the 103rd Sustainment
OL,8,FCommand, which provides food, fuel,
OL,9,Fwater, ammunition, transport equipment
OL,10,Fand supplies to forces.
OL,12,FAmong them were Capt. Cody Khork, 35,
OL,13,FSgt. 1st Class Nicole Amor, 39, Sgt.
OL,14,F1st Class Noah Tietjens, 42, and Chief
OL,15,FWarrant Officer 3 Robert M Marzan, 54,
OL,16,Fand Maj. Jeffrey R O'Brien, 45, who
OL,17,Fwere named in a separate statement.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
