OL,3,C'He was a baby': Sister of US soldier,
OL,4,C20, killed in Kuwait pays tribute
OL,6,FCoady's family had not been able to
OL,7,Fget hold of him on Sunday. When their
OL,8,Fdoorbell rang at 8pm they knew what it
OL,9,Fmeant, Keira said, calling it "one of
OL,10,Fthe worst nights of our lives".
OL,12,F"I still don't fully think it's real,
OL,13,FI didn't think it was real when they
OL,14,Ftold us," she said.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
