OL,3,C'He was a baby': Sister of US soldier,
OL,4,C20, killed in Kuwait pays tribute
OL,6,F"I just remember all of our
OL,7,Fconversations about what he was going
OL,8,Fto do when he came back."
OL,10,FIn a statement, Keira went on to say:
OL,11,F"He was just a baby, and will forever
OL,12,Fbe mine and Aidan's baby brother,
OL,13,FRowan's older brother, and our
OL,14,Fparents' son."
OL,16,FCoady enlisted in the Army Reserves in
OL,17,F2023, and was studying cybersecurity
OL,18,Fat Drake University in Des Moines,
OL,19,FIowa. The university described him as
OL,20,Fa "well-loved and highly dedicated"
OL,21,Fstudent in a statement.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
