OL,3,C'He was a baby': Sister of US soldier,
OL,4,C20, killed in Kuwait pays tribute
OL,6,FOne week ago, he told his father,
OL,7,FAndrew, he would be recommended for a
OL,8,Fpromotion from specialist to sergeant,
OL,9,Fa rank he has now been given
OL,10,Fposthumously.
OL,12,FHe was one of the youngest in his
OL,13,Fclass but seemed to impress his
OL,14,Finstructors, Andrew said.
OL,16,FCoady's LinkedIn page said he had
OL,17,Flearned to "interact with countless
OL,18,Fdifferent kinds of people from all
OL,19,Fdifferent backgrounds" through his
OL,20,Ftime with the Army Reserve.
OL,26,@yD@LOU{D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
