OL,3,C'He was a baby': Sister of US soldier,
OL,4,C20, killed in Kuwait pays tribute
OL,6,F"These men and women all bravely
OL,7,Fvolunteered to defend our country, and
OL,8,Ftheir sacrifice will never be
OL,9,Fforgotten," US Army Secretary Daniel
OL,10,FDriscoll said in a statement.
OL,12,FThe husband of Sgt. Amor paid tribute
OL,13,Fto the mum-of-two this week, stating
OL,14,Fthat she had been just days away from
OL,15,Freturning home to White Bear Lake,
OL,16,FMinnesota, when she was killed in
OL,17,FKuwait.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
