OL,3,C'He was a baby': Sister of US soldier,
OL,4,C20, killed in Kuwait pays tribute
OL,6,F"You don't go to Kuwait thinking
OL,7,Fsomething's going to happen, and for
OL,8,Fher to be one of the first ` it
OL,9,Fhurts," Joey Amor said.
OL,11,FTietjens, of Bellevue, Nebraska, was
OL,12,Fmarried with a son, according to his
OL,13,Fsocial media profiles, while one of
OL,14,FKhork's close friends posted on
OL,15,FFacebook that he had lost the best
OL,16,Fperson he had ever known.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
