OL,3,C'He was a baby': Sister of US soldier,
OL,4,C20, killed in Kuwait pays tribute
OL,6,FUS President Donald Trump said the US
OL,7,Fwill "avenge" US military deaths and
OL,8,Fdeliver a "punishing blow" to the Iran
OL,9,Fregime in a video posted to Truth
OL,10,FSocial on March 1.
OL,12,F"Sadly, there will likely be more
OL,13,Fbefore it ends. That's the way it is,"
OL,14,Fthe President said in the video.
OL,16,FAt least 1,045 people have died since
OL,17,FUS and Israeli strikes began on Iran,
OL,18,Faccording to Iran's Foundation of
OL,19,FMartyrs and Veterans Affairs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
